<main class="content">

  <!-- HERO -->
  <div class="hero">
    <div class="hero-eyebrow"><div class="hero-dot"></div>API Referansı — v2.0.0</div>
    <h1>Gemini Bot API</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Playwright tabanlı Gemini AI asistan REST API'si. Tam sohbet yönetimi, SSE streaming, aktivite analizi ve tarayıcı otomasyonu için tek endpoint.</p>
    <div class="hero-stats">
      <div class="stat-chip"><svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="color:var(--accent)"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="2" y1="12" x2="22" y2="12"/><path d="M12 2a15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4 10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1-4-10 15.3 15.3 0 0 1 4-10z"/></svg><span class="stat-chip-label">Base URL</span><span class="stat-chip-val">localhost:47371</span></div>
      <div class="stat-chip"><span class="stat-chip-label">Format</span><span class="stat-chip-val">JSON</span></div>
      <div class="stat-chip"><span class="stat-chip-label">Auth</span><span class="stat-chip-val">Bearer Token</span></div>
      <div class="stat-chip"><span class="stat-chip-label">Streaming</span><span class="stat-chip-val">SSE</span></div>
      <div class="stat-chip"><span class="stat-chip-label">Rate Limit</span><span class="stat-chip-val">60 req/dk</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- INTRO -->
  <div class="section" id="intro">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-icon"><svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 19.5A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 6.5 17H20"/><path d="M6.5 2H20v20H6.5A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 4 19.5v-15A2.5 2.5 0 0 1 6.5 2z"/></svg></div>
      <div class="section-title">Giriş</div>
      <span class="section-id">#intro</span>
    </div>
    <div class="info-box">
      <strong>Base URL:</strong> <code>http://localhost:47371</code><br><br>
      Tüm response'lar JSON formatındadır. Başarılı response'larda <code>"success": true</code> bulunur. Hatalı response'larda <code>"success": false</code> ve bir <code>"error"</code> string alanı döner.
    </div>
    <p>Bu API, Playwright kullanarak Gemini web arayüzünü otomasyonla kontrol eder. Google hesabına giriş yapılmış mevcut Chrome profilini kullanır — tamamen ücretsiz, Gemini API key gerektirmez.</p>
    <div class="code-block">
      <button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyCode(this)">Kopyala</button>
<span class="c-comment"># Başarılı response</span>
{ <span class="c-key">"success"</span>: <span class="c-val">true</span>, <span class="c-key">"data"</span>: { <span class="c-comment">/* endpoint'e özel */</span> } }

<span class="c-comment"># Hatalı response</span>
{ <span class="c-key">"success"</span>: <span class="c-val">false</span>, <span class="c-key">"error"</span>: <span class="c-str">"Hata mesajı"</span> }</div>
  </div>

  <!-- AUTH -->
  <div class="section" id="auth">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-icon"><svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2" ry="2"/><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"/></svg></div>
      <div class="section-title">Authentication</div>
      <span class="section-id">#auth</span>
    </div>
    <div class="warn-box">
      <svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="flex-shrink:0;margin-top:1px"><path d="M10.29 3.86L1.82 18a2 2 0 0 0 1.71 3h16.94a2 2 0 0 0 1.71-3L13.71 3.86a2 2 0 0 0-3.42 0z"/><line x1="12" y1="9" x2="12" y2="13"/><line x1="12" y1="17" x2="12.01" y2="17"/></svg>
      <span>Korumalı endpoint'lerde geçersiz veya eksik key gönderilirse <strong>401</strong> veya <strong>403</strong> döner.</span>
    </div>
    <div class="auth-grid">
      <div class="auth-card"><div class="auth-num">01 / AUTH HEADER</div><div class="auth-title">Authorization</div><div class="auth-desc">Bearer token şeması ile standart HTTP auth header.</div><span class="auth-badge rec">Önerilen</span></div>
      <div class="auth-card"><div class="auth-num">02 / CUSTOM HEADER</div><div class="auth-title">x-api-key</div><div class="auth-desc">Alternatif custom header, bazı istemcilerle daha kolay.</div><span class="auth-badge alt">Alternatif</span></div>
      <div class="auth-card"><div class="auth-num">03 / QUERY PARAM</div><div class="auth-title">api_key param</div><div class="auth-desc">URL query parametresi. Sadece test için kullan.</div><span class="auth-badge alt">Test</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="code-block">
      <button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyCode(this)">Kopyala</button>
<span class="c-comment"># Yöntem 1 (önerilen)</span>
Authorization: Bearer gmb_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

<span class="c-comment"># Yöntem 2</span>
x-api-key: gmb_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx

<span class="c-comment"># Yöntem 3 (sadece test)</span>
GET /api/stats?api_key=gmb_xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx</div>
    <div class="success-box">
      <svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="flex-shrink:0;margin-top:1px"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
      <span>Dashboard üzerinden <strong>/api/keys</strong> endpoint'i ile yeni key oluşturabilirsin. İlk çalıştırmada bir <strong>default</strong> key otomatik oluşturulur.</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ERRORS -->
  <div class="section" id="errors">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-icon"><svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/></svg></div>
      <div class="section-title">Hata Kodları</div>
      <span class="section-id">#errors</span>
    </div>
    <div class="error-grid">
      <div class="error-item e-2xx"><div class="error-code">200</div><div class="error-info"><div class="error-title">OK</div><div class="error-desc">İstek başarıyla tamamlandı</div></div></div>
      <div class="error-item e-4xx"><div class="error-code">400</div><div class="error-info"><div class="error-title">Bad Request</div><div class="error-desc">Eksik veya geçersiz parametre</div></div></div>
      <div class="error-item e-4xx"><div class="error-code">401</div><div class="error-info"><div class="error-title">Unauthorized</div><div class="error-desc">API key bulunamadı</div></div></div>
      <div class="error-item e-4xx"><div class="error-code">403</div><div class="error-info"><div class="error-title">Forbidden</div><div class="error-desc">Geçersiz API key</div></div></div>
      <div class="error-item e-4xx"><div class="error-code">404</div><div class="error-info"><div class="error-title">Not Found</div><div class="error-desc">Kaynak bulunamadı</div></div></div>
      <div class="error-item e-4xx"><div class="error-code">429</div><div class="error-info"><div class="error-title">Too Many Requests</div><div class="error-desc">Rate limit aşıldı</div></div></div>
      <div class="error-item e-5xx" style="grid-column:1/-1"><div class="error-code">500</div><div class="error-info"><div class="error-title">Internal Server Error</div><div class="error-desc">Sunucu tarafında beklenmedik hata</div></div></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- RATE LIMIT -->
  <div class="section" id="ratelimit">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-icon"><svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg></div>
      <div class="section-title">Rate Limiting</div>
      <span class="section-id">#ratelimit</span>
    </div>
    <div class="rate-visual">
      <div class="rate-bar-wrap">
        <span style="font-size:11px;color:var(--text2);min-width:80px">IP başına</span>
        <div class="rate-bar"><div class="rate-bar-fill"></div></div>
        <span class="rate-label">60 req/dk</span>
      </div>
      <div class="rate-info">Tüm <code style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;color:var(--accent);background:var(--glow2);padding:1px 5px;border-radius:4px">/api/*</code> endpoint'leri için geçerlidir. Limit aşılınca <code style="font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;color:var(--yellow);background:var(--yellow-bg);padding:1px 5px;border-radius:4px">429</code> döner.</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- HEALTH -->
  <div class="section" id="health">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-icon"><svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg></div>
      <div class="section-title">Health Check</div>
      <span class="section-id">#health</span>
    </div>
    <div class="endpoint open" id="ep-health">
      <div class="endpoint-header" onclick="toggleEp('ep-health')">
        <span class="ep-method get">GET</span><span class="ep-path">/api/health</span>
        <span class="ep-desc">Sunucu ve tarayıcı durumunu kontrol et</span>
        <span class="ep-auth pub">Public</span><span class="ep-chevron">▼</span>
      </div>
      <div class="endpoint-body">
        <div class="code-block"><button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyCode(this)">Kopyala</button>curl http://localhost:47371/api/health</div>
        <div class="ep-section-title">Response</div>
        <div class="response-chips"><span class="chip chip-ok">200 OK</span></div>
        <div class="code-block">{
  <span class="c-key">"success"</span>: <span class="c-val">true</span>,
  <span class="c-key">"status"</span>: <span class="c-str">"ok"</span>,
  <span class="c-key">"app"</span>: <span class="c-str">"Gemini Bot API"</span>,
  <span class="c-key">"version"</span>: <span class="c-str">"2.0.0"</span>,
  <span class="c-key">"browser"</span>: { <span class="c-key">"open"</span>: <span class="c-val">false</span>, <span class="c-key">"ready"</span>: <span class="c-val">false</span> },
  <span class="c-key">"timestamp"</span>: <span class="c-str">"2026-03-15T10:00:00.000Z"</span>
}</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- CHAT -->
  <div class="section" id="chat">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-icon"><svg width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/></svg></div>
      <div class="section-title">Chat</div>
      <span class="section-id">#chat</span>
    </div>

    <!-- /api/chat -->
    <div class="endpoint" id="ep-chat">
      <div class="endpoint-header" onclick="toggleEp('ep-chat')">
        <span class="ep-method post">POST</span><span class="ep-path">/api/chat</span>
        <span class="ep-desc">Gemini'ye mesaj gönder, tam yanıt bekle</span>
        <span class="ep-auth req">🔑 Auth</span><span class="ep-chevron">▼</span>
      </div>
      <div class="endpoint-body">
        <div class="ep-section-title">Request Body</div>
        <table>
          <tr><th>Alan</th><th>Tip</th><th>Zorunlu</th><th>Açıklama</th></tr>
          <tr><td><code>message</code></td><td>string</td><td><span class="req">*</span></td><td>Kullanıcı mesajı</td></tr>
          <tr><td><code>mode</code></td><td>string</td><td><span class="opt">—</span></td><td><code>chat</code> · <code>analyze</code> · <code>summarize</code> · <code>plan</code> · <code>code</code> · <code>debug</code></td></tr>
          <tr><td><code>activityIds</code></td><td>string[]</td><td><span class="opt">—</span></td><td>Bağlam için aktivite ID listesi</td></tr>
        </table>
        <div class="ep-section-title">Örnekler</div>
        <div class="tabs">
          <div class="tab active" onclick="switchTab(this,'chat-curl')">cURL</div>
          <div class="tab" onclick="switchTab(this,'chat-js')">JavaScript</div>
          <div class="tab" onclick="switchTab(this,'chat-analyze')">Analiz Modu</div>
        </div>
        <div id="chat-curl" class="tab-pane">
          <div class="code-block"><button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyCode(this)">Kopyala</button>curl -X POST http://localhost:47371/api/chat \
  -H <span class="c-str">"Authorization: Bearer gmb_xxxxx"</span> \
  -H <span class="c-str">"Content-Type: application/json"</span> \
  -d <span class="c-str">'{"message": "Merhaba!", "mode": "chat"}'</span></div>
        </div>
        <div id="chat-js" class="tab-pane" style="display:none">
          <div class="code-block"><button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyCode(this)">Kopyala</button><span class="c-key">const</span> res = <span class="c-key">await</span> fetch(<span class="c-str">"http://localhost:47371/api/chat"</span>, {
  method: <span class="c-str">"POST"</span>,
  headers: {
    <span class="c-str">"Authorization"</span>: <span class="c-str">"Bearer gmb_xxxxx"</span>,
    <span class="c-str">"Content-Type"</span>: <span class="c-str">"application/json"</span>
  },
  body: JSON.stringify({ message: <span class="c-str">"Merhaba!"</span>, mode: <span class="c-str">"chat"</span> })
});
<span class="c-key">const</span> { response } = <span class="c-key">await</span> res.json();</div>
        </div>
        <div id="chat-analyze" class="tab-pane" style="display:none">
          <div class="code-block"><button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyCode(this)">Kopyala</button>curl -X POST http://localhost:47371/api/chat \
  -H <span class="c-str">"Authorization: Bearer gmb_xxxxx"</span> \
  -H <span class="c-str">"Content-Type: application/json"</span> \
  -d <span class="c-str">'{"activityIds": ["id1","id2"], "mode": "analyze"}'</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="ep-section-title">Response</div>
        <div class="response-chips"><span class="chip chip-ok">200 OK</span><span class="chip chip-err">400</span><span class="chip chip-err">401</span></div>
        <div class="code-block">{
  <span class="c-key">"success"</span>: <span class="c-val">true</span>,
  <span class="c-key">"response"</span>: <span class="c-str">"## Analiz\n\nAktiviteleriniz incelenmiştir..."</span>,
  <span class="c-key">"responseTime"</span>: <span class="c-num">4231</span>
}</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- /api/chat/stream -->
    <div class="endpoint" id="ep-chat-stream" style="scroll-margin-top:24px">
      <div class="endpoint-header" onclick="toggleEp('ep-chat-stream')">
        <span class="ep-method post">POST</span><span class="ep-path">/api/chat/stream</span>
        <span class="ep-desc">Gerçek zamanlı SSE streaming yanıt</span>
        <span class="ep-auth req">🔑 Auth</span>
        <div class="ep-badge-sse">SSE</div>
        <span class="ep-chevron">▼</span>
      </div>
      <div class="endpoint-body">
        <div class="info-box" style="margin-bottom:14px">
          Bu endpoint <strong>Server-Sent Events (SSE)</strong> döndürür. <code>Content-Type: text/event-stream</code> header'ı ile gelir. Gemini yanıt yazarken her metin parçası ayrı bir <code>data:</code> satırı olarak akar; tamamlandığında <code>done: true</code> gönderilir.
        </div>
        <div class="ep-section-title">Request Body</div>
        <table>
          <tr><th>Alan</th><th>Tip</th><th>Zorunlu</th><th>Açıklama</th></tr>
          <tr><td><code>message</code></td><td>string</td><td><span class="req">*</span></td><td>Kullanıcı mesajı</td></tr>
          <tr><td><code>mode</code></td><td>string</td><td><span class="opt">—</span></td><td><code>chat</code> · <code>analyze</code> · <code>plan</code> · <code>code</code> · <code>debug</code></td></tr>
        </table>
        <div class="ep-section-title">Örnekler</div>
        <div class="tabs">
          <div class="tab active" onclick="switchTab(this,'stream-js')">JavaScript (EventSource)</div>
          <div class="tab" onclick="switchTab(this,'stream-fetch')">Fetch + ReadableStream</div>
        </div>
        <div id="stream-js" class="tab-pane">
          <div class="code-block"><button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyCode(this)">Kopyala</button><span class="c-comment">// EventSource sadece GET destekler; POST için fetch kullan</span>
<span class="c-key">const</span> res = <span class="c-key">await</span> fetch(<span class="c-str">"/api/chat/stream"</span>, {
  method: <span class="c-str">"POST"</span>,
  headers: {
    <span class="c-str">"Authorization"</span>: <span class="c-str">"Bearer gmb_xxxxx"</span>,
    <span class="c-str">"Content-Type"</span>: <span class="c-str">"application/json"</span>
  },
  body: JSON.stringify({ message: <span class="c-str">"Bana bir plan yaz"</span>, mode: <span class="c-str">"plan"</span> })
});

<span class="c-key">const</span> reader = res.body.getReader();
<span class="c-key">const</span> decoder = <span class="c-key">new</span> TextDecoder();

<span class="c-key">while</span> (<span class="c-val">true</span>) {
  <span class="c-key">const</span> { done, value } = <span class="c-key">await</span> reader.read();
  <span class="c-key">if</span> (done) <span class="c-key">break</span>;

  <span class="c-key">const</span> lines = decoder.decode(value).split(<span class="c-str">"\n"</span>);
  <span class="c-key">for</span> (<span class="c-key">const</span> line <span class="c-key">of</span> lines) {
    <span class="c-key">if</span> (!line.startsWith(<span class="c-str">"data: "</span>)) <span class="c-key">continue</span>;
    <span class="c-key">const</span> payload = JSON.parse(line.slice(<span class="c-num">6</span>));
    <span class="c-key">if</span> (payload.done) console.log(<span class="c-str">"Tamamlandı"</span>);
    <span class="c-key">else if</span> (payload.text) process.stdout.write(payload.text);
    <span class="c-key">else if</span> (payload.error) console.error(payload.error);
  }
}</div>
        </div>
        <div id="stream-fetch" class="tab-pane" style="display:none">
          <div class="code-block"><button class="copy-btn" onclick="copyCode(this)">Kopyala</button><span class="c-comment">// React / hook örneği</span>
<span class="c-key">async function</span> streamChat(message, onChunk, onDone) {
  <span class="c-key">const</span> res = <span class="c-key">await</span> fetch(<span class="c-str">"/api/chat/stream"</span>, {
    method: <span class="c-str">"POST"</span>,
    headers: {
      <span class="c-str">"Authorization"</span>: <span class="c-str">"Bearer gmb_xxxxx"</span>,
      <span class="c-str">"Content-Type"</span>: <span class="c-str">"application/json"</span>
    },
    body: JSON.stringify({ message })
  });

  <span class="c-key">const</span> reader = res.body.getReader();
  <span class="c-key">const</span> dec = <span class="c-key">new</span> TextDecoder();
  <span class="c-key">let</span> buf = <span class="c-str">""</span>;

  <span class="c-key">while</span> (<span class="c-val">true</span>) {
    <span class="c-key">const</span> { done, value } = <span class="c-key">await</span> reader.read();
    <span class="c-key">if</span> (done) <span class="c-key">break</span>;
    buf += dec.decode(value, { stream: <span class="c-val">true</span> });
    <span class="c-key">const</span> parts = buf.split(<span class="c-str">"\n\n"</span>);
    buf = parts.pop();
    <span class="c-key">for</span> (<span class="c-key">const</span> part <span class="c-key">of</span> parts) {
      <span class="c-key">if</span> (!part.startsWith(<span class="c-str">"data: "</span>)) <span class="c-key">continue</span>;
      <span class="c-key">const</span> p = JSON.parse(part.slice(<span class="c-num">6</span>));
      <span class="c-key">if</span> (p.text && !p.done) onChunk(p.text);
      <span class="c-key">if</span> (p.done) onDone(p.text);
    }
  }
}</div>
        </div>
        <div class="ep-section-title">SSE Event Formatı</div>
        <div class="code-block"><span class="c-comment"># Her chunk (Gemini yazarken)</span>
data: {"text": "Planlama sonuçları..."}

<span class="c-comment"># Tamamlandı</span>
data: {"done": true, "text": "Tüm yanıt metni"}

<span class="c-comment"># Hata</span>
data: {"error": "Tarayıcı bağlantısı kesildi"}</div>
      </div>
    </div>

